com.serena.dmclient.api
Class ScheduleJobDetails

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.api.ScheduleJobDetails

public class ScheduleJobDetails
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains details of a new schedule job that is to be created. It does not perform any validation, but is merely a data object to pass to the create schedule job, which will validate it and then act on it.
